@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Student: Create Found/Lost Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary

--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Lost Wallet
--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Black leather wallet lost near cafeteria
--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="item.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample/item.jpg
--WebKitFormBoundary--

### Public: List All Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/all

### Student: My Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/my
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Public: Post Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/{{POST_ID}}

### Student: Claim Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/{{POST_ID}}/claim
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Student: Update Post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/{{POST_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary

--WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Updated description
--WebKitFormBoundary--

### Student: Close Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/{{POST_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Admin: All Posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin: Update Post Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/admin/{{POST_ID}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Closed"
}

### Admin: Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/foundlost/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}


